{"tid":1793733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港超聯】冬至對東方入奠勝球 前港腳逆權手勢抗警暴","createTime":"2019-12-22T15:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:43:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e88c4b194dae7c5d4cf5c8158007cb8449a9ca62","tid":1793733,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191222/S3MFLKQBUZJ4IWSYDONM6JWFXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191222%2FS3MFLKQBUZJ4IWSYDONM6JWFXQ%2F&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=67ecb431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191222%2FS3MFLKQBUZJ4IWSYDONM6JWFXQ%2F&h=53103f76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191222/S3MFLKQBUZJ4IWSYDONM6JWFXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n【港超聯】冬至對東方入奠勝球 前港腳逆權手勢抗警暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191222/large/1577013144_aed1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191222%2Flarge%2F1577013144_aed1.jpg&h=4b6a2dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n顏樂楓入球後做出五大訴求手勢。<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n理文今午在港超聯憑隊長顏樂楓上半場補時階段建功，入球後除與隊友慶祝外，還不忘做出抗爭手勢，這名前港腳賽後未有正面回應做出「五加一」手勢的意思，只稱入球慶祝動作是抄襲其理文隊友余煒廉。然而，適逢今日冬至，但包括中環等多區均有出現警暴，顏樂楓早前曾因前隊友葉頌朗以督察身份接受央視訪問後，在社交平台暗指與這名兄弟割席，今次在球場做出抗爭手勢，似乎是對政府及警察的不滿作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【港超聯】顏樂楓奠勝 理文挫東方直追富力<br />\n<br />\n今季越戰越勇的理文，下午在港超聯前列戰收起部份主力仍能擊敗東方取得重要3分，入球功臣顏樂楓賽後表示，球隊在拆禮物日的銀牌四強對大埔，今仗能擊敗前列強隊東方，對球隊有提升信心，至於對爭標則沒有特別去想，因為今季目標是踢好每場，一步一步改善。問到他入球後所做出「五加一」慶祝動作，是否代表「五大訴求，缺一不可」時，他表示：「做這動作是抄隊友余煒廉早前的慶祝入球方式。」<br />\n<br />\n理文守衞余煒廉在銀牌八強對傑志射成2:0後，向球迷做出五加一手勢；這位前港青隊長賽後被問到入球做出的手勢有何意思時，他未有正面回應是否代表「五大訴求，缺一不可」，只稱要明白的人便會明白當中代表甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n雖然顏樂楓未有言明五加一手勢的意思，但他早前於社交平台指，看完其已為督察的前隊友葉頌朗接受央視訪問後，不開名與對方割席，並謂「曾經稱兄道弟，如今唯有各自修行」他於文末標註「割」字，似是意指從此與葉割席；似乎這位擁有大學學位的中場與不少手足屬同路人。<br />\n<br />\n記者、攝影：曾雁平"},{"pid":"37eadd2b2ea10159c8c63348c34f0586d64b5f32","tid":1793733,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d6ea440777714af9d457af47fa10ad181af780","tid":1793733,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">和你坐  Stuck稅局</span><br />\n12月23日 星期一<br />\n時間 : 12:00<br />\n地點 : 稅務大樓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">稅局聖誕激光燈飾之夜</span><br />\n19:00<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「星火不息 燃點國際」集會</span><br />\n日期︰2019年12月23日(一)<br />\n時間︰晚上七時至九時<br />\n地點︰中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦方︰張崑陽、候任中西區區議員梁晃維、民間集會團隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲警方發出不反對通知書</span>"},{"pid":"fd12230e6ec2bd7da85734766a98fbbf794b38e6","tid":1793733,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7e1e9907f1d6fe8790d380639037bed9b25d2a","tid":1793733,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"Respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係隊長"},{"pid":"a43dfe00ca18a3b9c3e4e3dadc4803cbaa4c449a","tid":1793733,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"清泉理<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306821724fdbb8452f379db8e28b2f798a74ccac","tid":1793733,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaa9898c1cb39209d32f230cdfcc4fea351d74f","tid":1793733,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2c29210facdab723821602b32994f9a0b4f523","tid":1793733,"uid":170812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:42:49.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<br />\n繼續踢好波"},{"pid":"1334ecabafb87b93be9d5d701dfb47314cc55cce","tid":1793733,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"理文好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cffc5d2f601c5c462ea739b62541a1b5297e240","tid":1793733,"uid":72991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"469a3b7a1404d28c8097be07cfdd208f62ed0b91","tid":1793733,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"}]}